data.description: SELLER OFFERING 2% CONCESSION FOR RATE BUY DOWN! This gorgeous like-new home is truly immaculate, with pride of ownership evident in every area! Spacious and open main floor with a covered patio - the perfect place to relax and unwind! Perfectly maintained, ample natural light, and modern finishes such as lovely LVP flooring, subway tile, central air conditioning, upstairs family lounge area, and overall excellent accommodation throughout the entire home. The low maintenance backyard is fully fenced and private. Convenient location, neighborhood park, great commute with I-5 nearby and just minutes from JBLM. Welcome Home!
